1
00:01:37,779 --> 00:01:39,980
I think you're swatting a fly on a tiger's head

2
00:01:40,139 --> 00:01:41,339
You must be tired of living

3
00:01:41,339 --> 00:01:43,260
I don't have time to waste with you

4
00:01:43,980 --> 00:01:44,820
Scram

5
00:01:52,339 --> 00:01:54,219
Misunderstanding, it's a misunderstanding

6
00:01:54,660 --> 00:01:56,180
We're just passing through, looking for someone

7
00:01:56,180 --> 00:01:56,980
Went the wrong way

8
00:01:57,980 --> 00:01:58,779
Kneel down

9
00:01:58,939 --> 00:02:00,020
Kneeling is a bit much

10
00:02:00,779 --> 00:02:01,380
Squat down

11
00:02:03,620 --> 00:02:04,939
What's up? What's up?

12
00:02:09,180 --> 00:02:10,339
What's the matter?

13
00:02:10,620 --> 00:02:11,540
I'll handle it

14
00:02:13,380 --> 00:02:14,380
He has a gun in his hand

15
00:02:14,739 --> 00:02:16,660
I saw it, it's a gun

16
00:02:16,780 --> 00:02:17,820
Can't win against that

17
00:02:19,260 --> 00:02:20,100
This whole thing...

18
00:02:20,459 --> 00:02:22,540
...was never our business anyway

19
00:02:23,220 --> 00:02:25,060
Open the umbrella, every man for himself

20
00:02:25,220 --> 00:02:26,940
How could we possibly leave you here?

21
00:02:28,220 --> 00:02:29,660
I'll go find two kitchen knives first

22
00:02:31,780 --> 00:02:33,060
I'll go find a hoe

23
00:02:47,940 --> 00:02:49,060
If you have treasure, offer it

24
00:02:49,060 --> 00:02:50,340
If no treasure, undergo the test

25
00:02:50,660 --> 00:02:51,820
Together we support the Han House

26
00:02:52,139 --> 00:02:53,459
Creating fortune and prosperity

27
00:02:54,340 --> 00:02:55,139
Here are my card and credentials

28
00:02:55,139 --> 00:02:56,100
Please receive them

29
00:02:56,179 --> 00:02:57,940
Gold plates, silver plates

30
00:02:58,019 --> 00:03:00,179
Brother offers treasure to brother

31
00:03:00,419 --> 00:03:02,179
If you accept this treasure, brother

32
00:03:02,220 --> 00:03:04,220
May you rise to sit in the eight-bearer sedan

33
00:03:04,820 --> 00:03:06,459
Which Dragon Wharf? Which chair do you sit in?

34
00:03:06,660 --> 00:03:08,060
My surname is Fan

35
00:03:08,060 --> 00:03:09,340
My given name is Pengju

36
00:03:09,459 --> 00:03:11,980
Weiyuan Yizi Hall, holding the Yao rank

37
00:03:12,019 --> 00:03:13,699
The flood has washed over the Dragon King's temple

38
00:03:14,060 --> 00:03:16,340
So, brother, you are also in the life

39
00:03:16,380 --> 00:03:17,179
My apologies, my apologies

40
00:03:18,859 --> 00:03:20,739
The person is sick like this

41
00:03:21,260 --> 00:03:23,859
Why beat a lame rabbit?

42
00:03:23,980 --> 00:03:24,820
Brother

43
00:03:25,060 --> 00:03:27,100
You want to raise the Banner of Brotherhood here

44
00:03:27,739 --> 00:03:28,619
If you want to raise the Banner of Brotherhood

45
00:03:28,619 --> 00:03:29,859
Then don't flake out

46
00:03:31,260 --> 00:03:32,220
How much does she owe you?

47
00:03:32,980 --> 00:03:35,060
She borrowed five silver dollars from our master

48
00:03:35,139 --> 00:03:36,419
Now with interest rolling over

49
00:03:36,459 --> 00:03:37,579
It's ten silver dollars

50
00:03:37,820 --> 00:03:39,859
Chengdu to Huayang, cash on the spot

51
00:03:39,940 --> 00:03:41,060
Luzhou crossing the river, a small matter

52
00:03:41,139 --> 00:03:42,260
Small matter

53
00:03:42,859 --> 00:03:43,660
I'll pay

54
00:03:46,060 --> 00:03:47,060
How much do you have here?

55
00:03:47,859 --> 00:03:49,019
One silver dollar

56
00:03:49,019 --> 00:03:51,660
Two thousand eight hundred and sixty coppers

57
00:03:52,980 --> 00:03:54,060
Not even enough for the principal

58
00:04:03,980 --> 00:04:05,019
Two porcelain jars

59
00:04:08,660 --> 00:04:09,579
A basket of vegetables

60
00:04:10,019 --> 00:04:11,619
Plus a chunk of cured meat

61
00:04:12,260 --> 00:04:13,540
What is this stuff?

62
00:04:13,579 --> 00:04:14,220
Who wants this?

63
00:04:32,179 --> 00:04:33,780
High-quality silk

64
00:04:34,340 --> 00:04:35,419
It's worth some money

65
00:04:41,739 --> 00:04:42,859
I don't need this anymore

66
00:04:44,660 --> 00:04:45,939
The account is still far off

67
00:04:47,419 --> 00:04:48,819
The account is still far off

68
00:04:52,859 --> 00:04:54,059
A Jianghu emergency

69
00:04:55,340 --> 00:04:57,059
I need to give my brother an explanation

70
00:05:28,819 --> 00:05:29,819
Respect

71
00:05:30,140 --> 00:05:31,140
Consider it done

72
00:05:45,220 --> 00:05:46,259
Brother

73
00:05:47,179 --> 00:05:48,460
Not giving me face?

74
00:05:56,259 --> 00:05:57,059
Brother

75
00:05:58,460 --> 00:05:59,379
You win

76
00:06:00,540 --> 00:06:01,900
Today, this Banner of Brotherhood

77
00:06:02,379 --> 00:06:03,220
Is yours to plant

78
00:06:05,379 --> 00:06:06,179
Let's split

79
00:06:12,859 --> 00:06:13,460
Brother Fan

80
00:06:13,660 --> 00:06:15,980
I will never forget your kindness

81
00:06:16,619 --> 00:06:18,059
Get up, get up, quick

82
00:06:18,419 --> 00:06:19,220
Get up

83
00:06:20,460 --> 00:06:24,059
I truly consider you my master

84
00:06:25,739 --> 00:06:27,259
Hold on, let me sit a bit

85
00:06:30,340 --> 00:06:31,100
Scarface

86
00:06:31,179 --> 00:06:32,580
You're playing the saint

87
00:06:32,660 --> 00:06:33,619
We didn't collect enough debt

88
00:06:33,739 --> 00:06:35,059
How do we report to the Boss?

89
00:06:35,059 --> 00:06:36,580
Money is a small matter

90
00:06:36,819 --> 00:06:37,859
How do I usually teach you?

91
00:06:38,419 --> 00:06:39,379
In the underworld

92
00:06:39,379 --> 00:06:40,419
Righteousness comes first

93
00:06:40,540 --> 00:06:42,059
Don't look at that fool acting silly

94
00:06:42,059 --> 00:06:43,540
He's loyal and has guts

95
00:06:43,780 --> 00:06:45,259
We who are in the life respect Guan Gong

96
00:06:45,259 --> 00:06:46,460
We can't give a hero a hard time

97
00:06:46,780 --> 00:06:48,460
But the Boss will give us a hard time

98
00:06:48,540 --> 00:06:50,059
The new guy from last month

99
00:06:50,140 --> 00:06:50,660
Didn't collect the debt

100
00:06:50,660 --> 00:06:52,259
Went back and got a leg broken

101
00:06:52,660 --> 00:06:54,220
We're short so much money this time

102
00:06:54,340 --> 00:06:55,739
I'm afraid someone's gonna die

103
00:06:57,900 --> 00:06:58,939
Then let's not go back for now

104
00:07:00,540 --> 00:07:01,540
So what do we do?

105
00:07:04,460 --> 00:07:05,460
Take it one step at a time

106
00:07:06,020 --> 00:07:06,939
What a disgrace

107
00:07:07,259 --> 00:07:08,660
You disgrace, you disgrace

108
00:07:09,220 --> 00:07:10,220
I told you to collect a debt

109
00:07:10,220 --> 00:07:11,819
And you come back looking like this

110
00:07:12,259 --> 00:07:14,499
You squandered all that money

111
00:07:15,259 --> 00:07:16,460
I ran into bandits

112
00:07:16,460 --> 00:07:17,619
What could I do?

113
00:07:17,660 --> 00:07:19,499
Bandits? I'm the bandit!

114
00:07:19,900 --> 00:07:20,619
Granduncle, Granduncle

115
00:07:21,179 --> 00:07:22,020
Granduncle

116
00:07:22,660 --> 00:07:25,700
The bandits beat me, now you want to beat me too?

117
00:07:25,780 --> 00:07:26,780
Go ahead and hit me

118
00:07:26,780 --> 00:07:28,980
The Fan family line will end

119
00:07:29,259 --> 00:07:31,660
Granduncle, if you want to hit someone, hit me

120
00:07:32,140 --> 00:07:33,379
He managed to come back alive

121
00:07:33,499 --> 00:07:34,660
That wasn't easy

122
00:07:34,700 --> 00:07:35,299
He...

123
00:07:35,739 --> 00:07:38,059
You believe that nonsense he says?

124
00:07:38,859 --> 00:07:39,939
I believe him

125
00:07:40,460 --> 00:07:42,299
Look at the state of him

126
00:07:42,660 --> 00:07:44,460
He was definitely bullied

127
00:07:44,780 --> 00:07:46,059
Just spare him

128
00:07:54,660 --> 00:07:57,020
I fought ten of them alone

129
00:07:57,220 --> 00:08:00,059
Good thing I practice usually

130
00:08:07,259 --> 00:08:08,619
Does it really hurt that much?

131
00:08:09,379 --> 00:08:11,220
If I didn't scream my head off

132
00:08:11,660 --> 00:08:13,220
Would Granduncle let me off?

133
00:08:14,059 --> 00:08:16,580
Good thing you were here today

134
00:08:16,859 --> 00:08:19,859
Otherwise I'd suffer without daring to make a sound

135
00:08:20,220 --> 00:08:21,220
Speak up

136
00:08:22,059 --> 00:08:22,859
Where's the money?

137
00:08:24,660 --> 00:08:25,580
Uh oh

138
00:08:25,980 --> 00:08:28,819
I married a sharp wife

139
00:08:29,179 --> 00:08:30,259
Confess honestly

140
00:08:33,259 --> 00:08:35,100
You went to pay someone else's debt

141
00:08:35,419 --> 00:08:36,739
Who did you pay for?

142
00:08:37,379 --> 00:08:38,180
Wen Yan

143
00:08:38,859 --> 00:08:39,659
Which Wen Yan?

144
00:08:40,019 --> 00:08:41,580
That opera singer Wen Yan

145
00:08:43,420 --> 00:08:44,539
Gently, please

146
00:08:45,019 --> 00:08:46,420
Wen Yan

147
00:08:46,739 --> 00:08:48,859
She's the star of the opera troupe

148
00:08:48,980 --> 00:08:51,460
She's the master I haven't bowed to yet

149
00:08:53,220 --> 00:08:55,060
You sure are loyal

150
00:08:55,220 --> 00:08:56,539
Of course

151
00:08:56,739 --> 00:08:58,060
When Master is in trouble

152
00:08:58,259 --> 00:09:00,340
The disciple will never flake out

153
00:09:03,220 --> 00:09:04,659
Then in your heart

154
00:09:05,980 --> 00:09:07,220
Is the master important

155
00:09:07,779 --> 00:09:09,460
Or is the wife important?

156
00:09:09,539 --> 00:09:10,139
Wife

157
00:09:10,580 --> 00:09:12,539
Heaven, Earth, Sovereign, Parent, Teacher

158
00:09:12,619 --> 00:09:14,300
You rank ahead of them all

159
00:09:17,539 --> 00:09:19,019
So, is she pretty?

160
00:09:19,580 --> 00:09:20,739
Not as pretty as you

161
00:09:24,659 --> 00:09:25,859
I don't believe a word you say

162
00:09:26,259 --> 00:09:28,060
Really not as pretty as you

163
00:09:38,259 --> 00:09:39,499
I had this made especially for you

164
00:09:39,700 --> 00:09:40,580
It's a gift

165
00:09:43,180 --> 00:09:44,220
It's a bit heavy

166
00:09:44,379 --> 00:09:45,420
You don't have to wear it

167
00:09:45,859 --> 00:09:47,779
Just keep it under your pillow

168
00:09:51,220 --> 00:09:51,779
All right

169
00:09:54,859 --> 00:09:57,100
You shouldn't go out anymore

170
00:09:57,379 --> 00:09:59,499
Don't worry about things outside

171
00:10:00,539 --> 00:10:03,460
Then what's the point of living?

172
00:10:04,460 --> 00:10:06,259
Just settle down and live with me

173
00:10:06,859 --> 00:10:07,580
Fine

174
00:10:07,580 --> 00:10:08,779
Tonight

175
00:10:08,779 --> 00:10:11,619
Let's enjoy our life together

176
00:10:13,539 --> 00:10:15,499
I should have let Patriarch Fan

177
00:10:15,499 --> 00:10:17,539
Give you a sound beating

178
00:10:17,619 --> 00:10:19,220
You wouldn't have the heart to

179
00:10:19,980 --> 00:10:22,100
You're hurt this bad already

180
00:10:22,859 --> 00:10:23,980
It won't get in the way, really

181
00:10:23,980 --> 00:10:24,700
Young Master

182
00:10:24,980 --> 00:10:26,460
The medicine Patriarch Fan ordered

183
00:10:31,340 --> 00:10:32,259
Darn it

184
00:10:32,259 --> 00:10:33,859
I'm not here, I'm not here

185
00:10:36,899 --> 00:10:37,739
It won't get in the way

186
00:10:38,340 --> 00:10:39,700
You really are...

187
00:11:13,700 --> 00:11:15,100
Something big has happened

188
00:11:19,300 --> 00:11:20,820
Gentlemen

189
00:11:21,019 --> 00:11:23,060
It's a disaster

190
00:11:23,220 --> 00:11:25,259
Something big has happened

191
00:11:25,259 --> 00:11:26,859
Don't rush, don't rush

192
00:11:26,980 --> 00:11:27,619
Sit down and speak

193
00:11:27,619 --> 00:11:28,899
Everyone sit down, sit down

194
00:11:32,340 --> 00:11:33,580
You have no idea

195
00:11:33,940 --> 00:11:35,980
In the dead of night yesterday

196
00:11:36,379 --> 00:11:38,019
Ma Laohu's bandits

197
00:11:38,259 --> 00:11:40,300
Barged into my humble home

198
00:11:40,580 --> 00:11:43,899
They looted all my stored grain

199
00:11:44,060 --> 00:11:45,460
They also want our town

200
00:11:45,460 --> 00:11:48,100
To scrape together a fixed quota

201
00:11:48,460 --> 00:11:50,060
Of money and grain as tribute every year

202
00:11:50,420 --> 00:11:51,859
If we don't pay up

203
00:11:52,180 --> 00:11:54,060
They'll start a massacre

204
00:11:54,460 --> 00:11:55,779
Before they left

205
00:11:56,139 --> 00:11:58,739
They even broke one of my legs

206
00:11:59,220 --> 00:12:01,139
This injury will take a hundred days to heal

207
00:12:01,139 --> 00:12:04,899
I know they're killing the chicken to scare the monkey

208
00:12:07,379 --> 00:12:09,580
Can you change to a different cat call?

209
00:12:09,899 --> 00:12:11,379
That cat of yours sounds awful

210
00:12:11,379 --> 00:12:12,180
I'll change it then

211
00:12:14,659 --> 00:12:15,259
This is a ghost wailing

212
00:12:15,259 --> 00:12:16,060
Wolf

213
00:12:16,139 --> 00:12:17,100
Young Master Fan

214
00:12:18,779 --> 00:12:20,300
Please accept our bow

215
00:12:20,460 --> 00:12:22,060
We greased our heels and fled back then

216
00:12:22,060 --> 00:12:23,820
Today we're here to apologize

217
00:12:23,820 --> 00:12:25,300
I can smash stones on my chest

218
00:12:25,300 --> 00:12:26,499
But I can't smash guns

219
00:12:26,619 --> 00:12:27,539
I can shoot sparrows

220
00:12:27,539 --> 00:12:28,580
But I can't shoot bullets

221
00:12:28,820 --> 00:12:31,180
Brother Fan, we let you down

222
00:12:31,539 --> 00:12:34,139
From now on, we brothers will train hard

223
00:12:34,460 --> 00:12:35,539
We won't embarrass you

224
00:12:35,659 --> 00:12:37,180
What are you doing?

225
00:12:37,659 --> 00:12:40,019
Get up, get up. We're all brothers here

226
00:12:40,220 --> 00:12:42,340
Master Wen was my business anyway

227
00:12:42,460 --> 00:12:44,420
It had nothing to do with you guys

228
00:12:46,739 --> 00:12:47,980
Did you see that?

229
00:12:48,820 --> 00:12:51,980
Young Master Fan really is magnanimous

230
00:12:52,220 --> 00:12:54,539
You are Zhao Zilong of Changbanpo

231
00:12:54,700 --> 00:12:56,580
You are Zhang Yide of Dangyang Bridge

232
00:12:56,659 --> 00:12:59,220
You are Guan Yunchang of the Five Passes and Six Generals

233
00:12:59,220 --> 00:13:02,700
You are our Big Brother Fan

234
00:13:05,300 --> 00:13:06,739
What Big Brother?

235
00:13:07,019 --> 00:13:08,379
Eldest Senior Brother is the Big Brother

236
00:13:08,580 --> 00:13:09,259
No, no, no

237
00:13:09,539 --> 00:13:12,379
You fought Scarface with a bear's heart and tiger's gall

238
00:13:12,379 --> 00:13:13,499
I am ashamed to be inferior

239
00:13:13,820 --> 00:13:14,619
From now on

240
00:13:14,619 --> 00:13:16,659
We brothers will follow your lead

241
00:13:18,379 --> 00:13:19,739
Brother Fan

242
00:13:20,580 --> 00:13:23,580
Your first task as Big Brother is quite tricky

243
00:13:23,659 --> 00:13:25,019
Now that these bandits are here

244
00:13:25,019 --> 00:13:27,180
Life was already tough for us brothers,

245
00:13:27,619 --> 00:13:29,259
and now it's gone from bad to worse.

246
00:13:32,899 --> 00:13:33,539
It's all your fault.

247
00:13:33,659 --> 00:13:35,820
When bandits rob the rich, you should stay away.

248
00:13:35,820 --> 00:13:36,940
But you called us over to watch the show.

249
00:13:37,019 --> 00:13:37,779
To gawk at the spectacle.

250
00:13:37,779 --> 00:13:38,460
Exactly.

251
00:13:38,460 --> 00:13:40,460
So the bandits robbed us too while they were at it.

252
00:13:40,619 --> 00:13:41,899
We hadn't collected enough debts to begin with,

253
00:13:41,899 --> 00:13:43,379
and now we have nothing left at all.

254
00:13:43,499 --> 00:13:45,300
How are we supposed to explain this to the boss?

255
00:13:45,499 --> 00:13:46,100
How was I supposed to know?

256
00:13:46,100 --> 00:13:47,460
That the famous Ma Laohu gang

257
00:13:47,700 --> 00:13:49,220
wouldn't even let small fry like us go?

258
00:13:49,460 --> 00:13:50,619
And you too, Scarface.

259
00:13:50,779 --> 00:13:52,139
When Ma Laohu's men were robbing us,

260
00:13:52,379 --> 00:13:53,379
you should have pulled your weapon.

261
00:13:54,820 --> 00:13:57,220
You lot are like old sows in a vegetable garden—

262
00:13:57,220 --> 00:13:58,379
all you know how to do is run your mouths.

263
00:13:59,019 --> 00:14:00,420
I've only got one gun.

264
00:14:00,420 --> 00:14:01,580
Ma Laohu has so many guns.

265
00:14:01,580 --> 00:14:02,700
You think I can outshoot them?

266
00:14:02,859 --> 00:14:04,820
We need to report this to the authorities.

267
00:14:05,300 --> 00:14:06,700
In times like these,

268
00:14:06,700 --> 00:14:08,580
those with guns make the rules.

269
00:14:08,619 --> 00:14:10,220
I'm afraid it might backfire on us.

270
00:14:10,220 --> 00:14:11,420
It won't.

271
00:14:11,700 --> 00:14:13,379
No matter how fierce the bandits are,

272
00:14:13,379 --> 00:14:15,300
they're still afraid of the army.

273
00:14:15,499 --> 00:14:17,820
Straw sandal fees, ammo fees, pursuit fees...

274
00:14:17,980 --> 00:14:19,619
They'll fleece you for a fortune first.

275
00:14:19,700 --> 00:14:20,899
Once the soldiers have had their fill

276
00:14:20,899 --> 00:14:22,060
and leave,

277
00:14:22,060 --> 00:14:23,820
Ma Laohu will come back for revenge.

278
00:14:23,899 --> 00:14:25,700
That's what you call a double whammy—

279
00:14:25,700 --> 00:14:27,300
suffering at both ends.

280
00:14:27,739 --> 00:14:29,060
So what do we do?

281
00:14:29,100 --> 00:14:30,300
I'll volunteer myself.

282
00:14:30,779 --> 00:14:32,100
I'll go negotiate with the bandits.

283
00:14:32,420 --> 00:14:34,180
They've always been honorable.

284
00:14:34,300 --> 00:14:36,019
If we can buy some peace and quiet,

285
00:14:36,180 --> 00:14:37,139
paying a little tribute

286
00:14:37,420 --> 00:14:38,220
is nothing.

287
00:14:38,659 --> 00:14:40,060
If you ask me,

288
00:14:40,100 --> 00:14:41,100
rather than taking this money and grain

289
00:14:41,100 --> 00:14:43,700
and letting Ma Laohu's bandits waste it,

290
00:14:43,859 --> 00:14:46,940
we'd be better off offering it to Commander Liao

291
00:14:47,220 --> 00:14:48,700
in exchange for his protection.

292
00:14:49,060 --> 00:14:50,499
They've all got fangs.

293
00:14:50,580 --> 00:14:51,859
There isn't one that doesn't eat people.

294
00:14:52,100 --> 00:14:53,899
They've been suppressing bandits for years,

295
00:14:54,100 --> 00:14:55,499
but have they ever wiped them out?

296
00:14:55,820 --> 00:14:57,899
It's like getting married on a theater stage—

297
00:14:58,420 --> 00:14:59,659
it's all just for show.

298
00:15:01,700 --> 00:15:03,100
Patriarch Fan,

299
00:15:03,420 --> 00:15:05,259
you're a respected elder here.

300
00:15:05,779 --> 00:15:07,379
You have to come up with a plan for us.

301
00:15:07,659 --> 00:15:09,700
Give us some advice.

302
00:15:21,700 --> 00:15:23,580
Why does this thunder keep crashing?

303
00:15:23,980 --> 00:15:24,700
Fan Bao.

304
00:15:25,420 --> 00:15:26,220
You go take a look.

305
00:15:26,220 --> 00:15:27,220
What's the matter?

306
00:15:27,300 --> 00:15:28,100
Okay.

307
00:15:32,499 --> 00:15:33,420
Patriarch.

308
00:15:33,859 --> 00:15:35,060
Where am I supposed to look?

309
00:15:35,100 --> 00:15:36,300
If I knew where to look...

310
00:15:36,300 --> 00:15:37,460
why would I be asking you?

311
00:15:40,420 --> 00:15:42,300
Now we'll have to be beggars.

312
00:15:42,820 --> 00:15:43,619
Scarface.

313
00:15:43,700 --> 00:15:45,460
How about we go to the opera house again?

314
00:15:45,619 --> 00:15:47,420
Maybe we'll run into that fat kid from last time.

315
00:15:47,420 --> 00:15:48,460
Judging by his looks,

316
00:15:48,460 --> 00:15:49,619
he must come from money.

317
00:15:49,700 --> 00:15:50,700
We'll make him cough up more cash.

318
00:15:50,700 --> 00:15:52,100
Anyway, he didn't give enough last time.

319
00:15:52,220 --> 00:15:53,420
What are you talking about?

320
00:15:54,300 --> 00:15:55,659
I'm a man of the world.

321
00:15:55,659 --> 00:15:57,019
A deal is a deal.

322
00:15:57,019 --> 00:15:58,060
I never go back on my word.

323
00:15:58,580 --> 00:15:59,820
You're so honorable.

324
00:15:59,820 --> 00:16:00,899
We don't have any money now.

325
00:16:01,300 --> 00:16:02,460
We really are going to have to beg.

326
00:16:02,659 --> 00:16:03,779
If the Master finds out,

327
00:16:03,859 --> 00:16:05,899
we won't live long enough to beg.

328
00:16:12,100 --> 00:16:14,060
Ma Laohu and those bandits...

329
00:16:14,060 --> 00:16:16,100
always act so brazenly.

330
00:16:16,300 --> 00:16:17,499
And they get away with it.

331
00:16:18,100 --> 00:16:19,300
That is because

332
00:16:19,300 --> 00:16:20,859
no one recognizes them.

333
00:16:21,379 --> 00:16:23,300
No one knows where they're from,

334
00:16:23,980 --> 00:16:24,940
nor do they know

335
00:16:24,940 --> 00:16:26,980
where they hide out.

336
00:16:27,499 --> 00:16:28,460
Every time they pull a job,

337
00:16:28,619 --> 00:16:29,700
they leave the word "Ma".

338
00:16:30,220 --> 00:16:32,300
To show it was Ma Laohu's crew.

339
00:16:32,619 --> 00:16:33,420
Unlike us.

340
00:16:33,420 --> 00:16:34,899
Scared to leave a single trace.

341
00:16:35,060 --> 00:16:36,460
How can you compare us

342
00:16:36,460 --> 00:16:37,580
to those bandits?

343
00:16:38,019 --> 00:16:39,499
We're different from them.

344
00:16:39,619 --> 00:16:40,580
What's different?

345
00:16:40,820 --> 00:16:42,300
We can be the same.

346
00:16:42,379 --> 00:16:43,899
Relying on bandits for troops

347
00:16:44,100 --> 00:16:46,060
is like drinking poison to quench thirst.

348
00:16:46,220 --> 00:16:48,420
The backlash is extremely dangerous.

349
00:16:48,619 --> 00:16:50,899
Better to reorganize the militia.

350
00:16:51,019 --> 00:16:52,619
Better to rely on oneself than others.

351
00:16:52,859 --> 00:16:54,940
Each family contributes troops for self-defense.

352
00:16:55,100 --> 00:16:57,300
To escape the grip of soldiers and bandits.

353
00:16:57,460 --> 00:16:58,700
Darn it.

354
00:16:59,220 --> 00:17:00,100
We'll just have to go rob someone.

355
00:17:00,499 --> 00:17:01,700
Keep it down, keep it down.

356
00:17:01,859 --> 00:17:02,980
To cover this debt.

357
00:17:02,980 --> 00:17:04,420
Then wouldn't we be bandits?

358
00:17:04,779 --> 00:17:05,820
We'll disguise ourselves as bandits.

359
00:17:06,300 --> 00:17:07,379
Bandits are robbing us,

360
00:17:07,499 --> 00:17:09,420
so we'll let them take the blame.

361
00:17:09,420 --> 00:17:10,099
Do you understand?

362
00:17:10,099 --> 00:17:11,220
They rob openly,

363
00:17:11,220 --> 00:17:12,299
we steal secretly.

364
00:17:12,299 --> 00:17:13,220
This obviously isn't

365
00:17:13,220 --> 00:17:14,499
how bandits operate.

366
00:17:14,499 --> 00:17:16,099
Who says bandits can't steal?

367
00:17:16,900 --> 00:17:17,620
Boss.

368
00:17:19,180 --> 00:17:21,539
We can also leave a "Ma" character.

369
00:17:22,860 --> 00:17:24,180
Let those bastard bandits

370
00:17:24,900 --> 00:17:25,900
take the fall no matter what.

371
00:17:26,099 --> 00:17:26,779
Also,

372
00:17:27,299 --> 00:17:29,579
notify the young men of every clan.

373
00:17:29,860 --> 00:17:31,299
Restate the clan rules.

374
00:17:31,420 --> 00:17:32,620
No matter who it is,

375
00:17:33,380 --> 00:17:35,460
anyone who becomes a bandit will be beheaded.

376
00:17:36,019 --> 00:17:36,819
Colluding with bandits,

377
00:17:37,180 --> 00:17:37,980
buried alive.

378
00:17:38,299 --> 00:17:38,980
Right.

379
00:17:39,339 --> 00:17:41,099
Harsh times call for harsh laws.

380
00:17:41,420 --> 00:17:42,739
Whatever plan you have, Boss,

381
00:17:43,220 --> 00:17:45,420
we'll do whatever you say.

382
00:17:45,579 --> 00:17:46,380
Brother Fan.

383
00:17:47,019 --> 00:17:48,059
Brother Fan.

384
00:17:48,420 --> 00:17:50,220
In these lean years,

385
00:17:50,220 --> 00:17:51,499
bandits are everywhere.

386
00:17:51,700 --> 00:17:53,380
Warlords are carving up the land.

387
00:17:55,579 --> 00:17:57,620
Total chaos is coming.

388
00:17:57,900 --> 00:17:59,779
The world is descending into chaos again.

389
00:18:06,220 --> 00:18:08,019
Bow to Heaven, Earth, and Guan Gong

390
00:18:08,140 --> 00:18:09,860
Betray the brothers and you'll suffer

391
00:18:09,860 --> 00:18:11,460
Loyalty and courage shine like the sun and moon

392
00:18:11,460 --> 00:18:13,019
Greenwood heroes shed their hot blood

393
00:18:13,019 --> 00:18:15,019
Kill the rich, help the poor, the Brotherhood

394
00:18:15,019 --> 00:18:17,460
The poor folks all say it's right

395
00:18:17,460 --> 00:18:18,299
Right

396
00:18:22,140 --> 00:18:22,940
Brothers

397
00:18:23,299 --> 00:18:24,299
Let's discuss this

398
00:18:24,579 --> 00:18:25,779
Which rich family is suitable?

399
00:18:25,779 --> 00:18:27,299
In my opinion, the Wang family

400
00:18:27,299 --> 00:18:28,299
That won't do

401
00:18:28,499 --> 00:18:30,220
Old Man Wang just got his leg broken

402
00:18:30,220 --> 00:18:32,299
Going again would break the rules of the Jianghu

403
00:18:32,299 --> 00:18:33,700
I think we should go to the Qian family

404
00:18:33,819 --> 00:18:34,819
The Qian family has lots of money

405
00:18:34,819 --> 00:18:35,620
The Qian family

406
00:18:35,620 --> 00:18:37,019
The Qians have many people and many dogs

407
00:18:37,220 --> 00:18:38,099
And guns too

408
00:18:38,099 --> 00:18:39,940
Why smash an egg against a rock?

409
00:18:40,019 --> 00:18:40,900
If you ask me

410
00:18:40,900 --> 00:18:41,700
The Ji family

411
00:18:41,860 --> 00:18:42,980
The Ji family's walls are low

412
00:18:42,980 --> 00:18:43,900
Easier to climb over

413
00:18:44,140 --> 00:18:45,140
I won't do it

414
00:18:45,420 --> 00:18:46,460
Grandma Ji, when I was little

415
00:18:46,460 --> 00:18:47,700
She washed my diapers

416
00:18:48,099 --> 00:18:49,620
I say, the Chen family

417
00:18:49,620 --> 00:18:51,299
The dog hole is big, easy to crawl through

418
00:18:51,380 --> 00:18:52,660
Discussing like this

419
00:18:52,819 --> 00:18:54,220
We won't have a result by tomorrow morning

420
00:18:54,420 --> 00:18:55,700
Big Brother, be decisive

421
00:18:55,700 --> 00:18:57,220
Fine, stop talking

422
00:18:57,380 --> 00:18:58,819
Let's settle it with a finger game

423
00:18:59,299 --> 00:19:00,700
You represent the Wang family

424
00:19:01,059 --> 00:19:02,460
You represent the Qian family

425
00:19:02,739 --> 00:19:04,059
You represent the Ji family

426
00:19:04,299 --> 00:19:05,700
You represent the Chen family

427
00:19:05,739 --> 00:19:07,579
I'll represent our Fan family

428
00:19:07,779 --> 00:19:08,660
Whoever loses

429
00:19:08,900 --> 00:19:10,059
That's the family we rob

430
00:19:10,059 --> 00:19:11,099
Deal, deal

431
00:19:11,099 --> 00:19:11,980
Come on, come on

432
00:19:12,579 --> 00:19:13,739
Random chopping!

433
00:19:13,739 --> 00:19:14,739
Eight horses!

434
00:19:14,739 --> 00:19:15,860
Five leaders!

435
00:19:16,140 --> 00:19:16,819
You lost

436
00:19:17,499 --> 00:19:18,660
Random chopping!

437
00:19:18,660 --> 00:19:19,579
Two brothers good!

438
00:19:20,220 --> 00:19:21,420
You're done for, you're done for

439
00:19:21,900 --> 00:19:23,099
Random chopping!

440
00:19:23,099 --> 00:19:24,220
Eight horses

441
00:19:24,700 --> 00:19:25,980
You're done for again

442
00:19:26,299 --> 00:19:27,700
Random chopping!

443
00:19:27,700 --> 00:19:28,900
Blow on empty!

444
00:19:28,900 --> 00:19:30,059
Little Sister Seven is cute!

445
00:19:30,059 --> 00:19:31,420
All have it!

446
00:19:31,420 --> 00:19:32,460
You lost

447
00:19:32,460 --> 00:19:33,860
Rob the Fan family

448
00:19:34,700 --> 00:19:35,299
Rob the Fan family

449
00:19:35,579 --> 00:19:37,299
What? Rob the Fan family?

450
00:19:38,220 --> 00:19:40,299
Big Brother, how about this doesn't count?

451
00:19:40,299 --> 00:19:41,099
Let's play another round

452
00:19:41,180 --> 00:19:42,499
What do you mean doesn't count?

453
00:19:42,620 --> 00:19:44,339
Brothers, hearts aligned

454
00:19:44,339 --> 00:19:47,019
Children of the Jianghu never flake out

455
00:19:48,059 --> 00:19:49,499
We rob whoever loses

456
00:19:49,499 --> 00:19:50,819
We agreed on it

457
00:19:51,380 --> 00:19:52,420
My family

458
00:19:52,860 --> 00:19:53,980
Has lots of grain

459
00:19:54,099 --> 00:19:55,259
Most importantly

460
00:19:55,620 --> 00:19:56,940
Robbing my own house

461
00:19:57,700 --> 00:19:59,059
It's not easy to get caught

462
00:19:59,499 --> 00:20:00,779
We'll listen to Big Brother

463
00:20:01,259 --> 00:20:02,220
Good

464
00:20:07,499 --> 00:20:10,380
You're the only one here who can handle a gun or stick

465
00:20:11,819 --> 00:20:13,220
If you encounter any situation

466
00:20:14,019 --> 00:20:15,700
Fire a warning shot

467
00:20:16,860 --> 00:20:18,059
The town militia

468
00:20:18,499 --> 00:20:20,019
Will rush to the rescue

469
00:20:20,339 --> 00:20:21,420
When night falls

470
00:20:22,299 --> 00:20:23,700
Lock the front door

471
00:20:24,099 --> 00:20:25,259
Bar the back door

472
00:20:25,779 --> 00:20:28,460
You arrange the night watch

473
00:20:29,259 --> 00:20:30,059
Will do

474
00:20:31,499 --> 00:20:32,739
Give me the gun

475
00:20:37,299 --> 00:20:39,099
Yes, sir

476
00:20:50,019 --> 00:20:51,420
You must remember

477
00:20:52,860 --> 00:20:54,700
I'll watch the first half of the night

478
00:20:55,299 --> 00:20:56,819
You watch the second half

479
00:20:57,620 --> 00:20:59,499
Why don't we watch together?

480
00:20:59,819 --> 00:21:00,980
Who wants to watch with you?

481
00:21:01,499 --> 00:21:04,220
In the second half, I'll be sleepy

482
00:21:05,700 --> 00:21:07,019
Give me the gun

483
00:21:09,059 --> 00:21:11,860
You caught too many sparrows as a kid, your hand shakes

484
00:21:11,860 --> 00:21:13,099
It's easy to misfire

485
00:21:15,099 --> 00:21:16,380
Your hands are shaking too

486
00:21:30,259 --> 00:21:31,220
Oh no, oh no

487
00:21:31,220 --> 00:21:32,579
Senior Brother, someone's coming

488
00:21:32,579 --> 00:21:33,420
Someone's coming

489
00:21:58,860 --> 00:21:59,900
How could it be him?

490
00:22:02,259 --> 00:22:03,700
Didn't you scout it out already?

491
00:22:03,980 --> 00:22:05,019
We've walked this way so many times.

492
00:22:05,019 --> 00:22:06,019
Which house are we stealing from anyway?

493
00:22:07,259 --> 00:22:08,140
This place in the daytime versus at night...

494
00:22:08,140 --> 00:22:09,299
...looks completely different.

495
00:22:09,539 --> 00:22:11,059
What do I need you for?

496
00:22:23,460 --> 00:22:24,980
Heaven helps me.

497
00:22:25,620 --> 00:22:26,779
Ma Laohu

498
00:22:27,380 --> 00:22:29,019
You're definitely taking the blame for this.

499
00:22:37,460 --> 00:22:38,259
Don't move.

500
00:22:40,259 --> 00:22:41,259
Hands up.

501
00:22:42,380 --> 00:22:43,180
Get down.

502
00:22:51,819 --> 00:22:53,539
Why did you come so late?

503
00:22:54,059 --> 00:22:54,700
Go.

504
00:22:54,860 --> 00:22:56,299
Straight into the granary.

505
00:22:56,739 --> 00:22:57,380
Go.

506
00:22:59,819 --> 00:23:00,620
Go.

507
00:23:11,940 --> 00:23:13,660
Why did Brother Fan change his mind?

508
00:23:14,299 --> 00:23:15,299
Playing with them...

509
00:23:15,980 --> 00:23:17,140
...and not playing with us anymore?

510
00:23:17,700 --> 00:23:18,819
You fool.

511
00:23:41,539 --> 00:23:42,980
Everyone go hide for a few days.

512
00:23:43,420 --> 00:23:46,180
If anything happens, I'll take the heat.

513
00:23:46,900 --> 00:23:48,220
Don't say a word.

514
00:23:48,380 --> 00:23:49,259
Go.

515
00:24:02,019 --> 00:24:04,059
Why is "bed" written there?

516
00:24:19,620 --> 00:24:21,660
Are you going to confess now?

517
00:24:22,019 --> 00:24:23,660
It's him.

518
00:24:23,660 --> 00:24:24,900
Who?

519
00:24:25,380 --> 00:24:27,220
Those thieves.

520
00:24:27,220 --> 00:24:29,579
I don't recognize a single one.

521
00:24:29,900 --> 00:24:32,900
I only recognize the Young Master.

522
00:24:32,900 --> 00:24:34,940
Did you see clearly?

523
00:24:35,019 --> 00:24:37,099
It is him.

524
00:24:38,019 --> 00:24:40,660
My butt! My butt!

525
00:24:42,700 --> 00:24:43,660
Sha'er.

526
00:24:45,860 --> 00:24:46,940
Sha'er.

527
00:24:48,579 --> 00:24:50,180
You've committed a serious crime.

528
00:24:50,180 --> 00:24:51,299
What is it?

529
00:24:52,099 --> 00:24:53,980
Fan Bao confessed everything.

530
00:24:54,499 --> 00:24:56,259
Tell me, why are you so stupid?

531
00:24:56,259 --> 00:24:57,140
You help others...

532
00:24:57,339 --> 00:24:58,900
...move grain from your own house.

533
00:24:59,220 --> 00:25:00,900
My family has plenty of grain.

534
00:25:01,460 --> 00:25:03,299
Giving away some unhusked rice is no big deal.

535
00:25:03,900 --> 00:25:05,700
Rules were set this time.

536
00:25:06,099 --> 00:25:08,700
It's either beheading or being buried alive.

537
00:25:09,059 --> 00:25:11,099
I don't believe Patriarch Fan would tell me to die.

538
00:25:11,499 --> 00:25:12,099
Come on.

539
00:25:12,299 --> 00:25:13,019
Come on, let's play a bit.

540
00:25:13,900 --> 00:25:15,299
Get up.

541
00:25:16,700 --> 00:25:18,099
You sure are carefree.

542
00:25:18,620 --> 00:25:19,900
Hurry up and go see Patriarch Fan.

543
00:25:20,019 --> 00:25:21,739
Confess who your accomplices are.

544
00:25:22,140 --> 00:25:23,140
Maybe Patriarch Fan...

545
00:25:23,779 --> 00:25:24,860
...will still spare you.

546
00:25:25,059 --> 00:25:26,299
How can I do that?

547
00:25:26,940 --> 00:25:29,299
Children of the Jianghu never flake out.

548
00:25:29,539 --> 00:25:30,940
How would I get by in the future?

549
00:25:31,660 --> 00:25:33,499
Can't you just make up a few names...

550
00:25:33,739 --> 00:25:34,900
...to hold them off for now?

551
00:25:34,980 --> 00:25:36,220
Young Master.

552
00:25:39,059 --> 00:25:40,220
Young Master.

553
00:25:40,420 --> 00:25:42,339
The Patriarch wants to see you.

554
00:25:43,180 --> 00:25:45,460
You son of a turtle, you dog.

555
00:25:45,460 --> 00:25:47,579
You disgraceful sellout! I...

556
00:25:47,739 --> 00:25:48,380
Kick.

557
00:25:48,940 --> 00:25:49,620
One kick.

558
00:25:50,700 --> 00:25:52,099
You betrayed me!

559
00:25:52,140 --> 00:25:53,499
I know you're not happy with me.

560
00:25:53,499 --> 00:25:54,940
Don't kick here.

561
00:25:54,940 --> 00:25:56,180
Kick here instead.

562
00:25:56,180 --> 00:25:57,220
Here, kick however you want.

563
00:25:57,220 --> 00:25:58,180
Here, kick any way you like.

564
00:25:58,180 --> 00:25:59,299
Damn it.

565
00:26:00,700 --> 00:26:01,380
Stand still.

566
00:26:01,660 --> 00:26:02,380
Stand still for me!

567
00:26:02,380 --> 00:26:04,140
What's the use of hitting him?

568
00:26:05,339 --> 00:26:06,140
Patriarch.

569
00:26:06,140 --> 00:26:07,539
Help me, Patriarch!

570
00:26:08,779 --> 00:26:09,579
Stand still.

571
00:26:11,180 --> 00:26:13,299
He and I were just messing around.

572
00:26:13,299 --> 00:26:15,739
Messing around? Was it you...

573
00:26:19,019 --> 00:26:20,539
...and who else?

574
00:26:25,299 --> 00:26:26,339
There's Fan Bao

575
00:26:27,700 --> 00:26:28,860
Patriarch, not me

576
00:26:28,860 --> 00:26:29,779
Not me

577
00:26:30,460 --> 00:26:31,259
Zhang Mangzi

578
00:26:31,499 --> 00:26:32,700
Young Master, don't talk nonsense

579
00:26:32,700 --> 00:26:33,739
How am I involved?

580
00:26:33,739 --> 00:26:34,420
Tong Wazi

581
00:26:34,700 --> 00:26:35,779
I'm not in it

582
00:26:35,779 --> 00:26:36,620
Qin Dahan'er

583
00:26:36,620 --> 00:26:37,259
Young Master

584
00:26:37,259 --> 00:26:38,339
It's not me

585
00:26:38,499 --> 00:26:39,299
Mama Zhang

586
00:26:39,739 --> 00:26:40,779
Not me, not me

587
00:26:40,779 --> 00:26:42,180
They were all involved

588
00:26:43,180 --> 00:26:44,739
Absolute rubbish!

589
00:26:44,860 --> 00:26:46,059
The way you put it,

590
00:26:46,059 --> 00:26:47,339
my house of scholars

591
00:26:47,339 --> 00:26:49,980
has become a den of thieves!

592
00:26:50,259 --> 00:26:50,900
You said not to say it

593
00:26:50,900 --> 00:26:52,339
So I won't say it

594
00:26:52,980 --> 00:26:55,499
You'll be the death of me

595
00:26:55,499 --> 00:26:57,900
Patriarch Fan, don't get too worked up

596
00:26:58,059 --> 00:27:00,339
Just give him a beating and be done with it

597
00:27:00,579 --> 00:27:03,059
Patriarch Fan, don't be angry either

598
00:27:03,380 --> 00:27:05,180
Your eagerness to protect your grandson,

599
00:27:05,539 --> 00:27:06,819
we all understand clearly

600
00:27:07,099 --> 00:27:08,499
To be honest,

601
00:27:08,660 --> 00:27:10,660
if one's own son made a mistake,

602
00:27:11,059 --> 00:27:12,380
wouldn't one want to...

603
00:27:12,380 --> 00:27:14,299
This isn't a mistake

604
00:27:14,499 --> 00:27:16,059
This is a crime

605
00:27:18,579 --> 00:27:21,059
If it were our children,

606
00:27:22,180 --> 00:27:23,420
Patriarch Fan,

607
00:27:23,420 --> 00:27:26,059
I'm afraid you'd handle it impartially

608
00:27:29,220 --> 00:27:31,380
What the hell are you saying?

609
00:27:31,660 --> 00:27:32,900
Do you have any idea?

610
00:27:33,059 --> 00:27:34,539
For miles around here,

611
00:27:34,539 --> 00:27:36,579
Patriarch Fan is highly respected

612
00:27:36,860 --> 00:27:37,980
His word carries weight

613
00:27:38,099 --> 00:27:40,299
He is the representative of fairness and justice

614
00:27:40,940 --> 00:27:42,299
He means what he says

615
00:27:42,299 --> 00:27:44,460
How could he have double standards?

616
00:27:44,700 --> 00:27:48,140
If we all acted on emotion and not reason,

617
00:27:48,180 --> 00:27:49,739
then this town of ours

618
00:27:49,739 --> 00:27:51,140
would have fallen apart long ago

619
00:27:56,019 --> 00:27:57,339
I'll ask you one more time

620
00:27:58,299 --> 00:28:00,299
That 'Ma' character on the backyard wall,

621
00:28:00,700 --> 00:28:02,220
did you write it?

622
00:28:03,660 --> 00:28:05,460
I wrote it for fun

623
00:28:06,140 --> 00:28:06,980
So what?

624
00:28:07,660 --> 00:28:09,180
Is writing a crime now?

625
00:28:09,980 --> 00:28:12,180
Just wrote it for fun

626
00:28:14,099 --> 00:28:14,980
Lock him up!

627
00:28:18,019 --> 00:28:18,660
What?

628
00:28:18,860 --> 00:28:20,900
What, what, what?

629
00:28:22,420 --> 00:28:23,299
Granduncle

630
00:28:23,700 --> 00:28:25,779
Are you really going to be ruthless?

631
00:28:27,539 --> 00:28:29,180
Handle it impartially?

632
00:28:30,019 --> 00:28:30,739
Fine

633
00:28:31,019 --> 00:28:31,700
Fine

634
00:28:31,700 --> 00:28:33,140
You can't do this!

635
00:28:33,700 --> 00:28:35,460
You can't do this!

636
00:28:41,380 --> 00:28:42,299
Everyone,

637
00:28:43,180 --> 00:28:45,339
right here and now,

638
00:28:46,220 --> 00:28:47,940
the times are chaotic,

639
00:28:48,860 --> 00:28:50,380
with trouble inside and out.

640
00:28:51,579 --> 00:28:53,900
Today, in this small town of ours,

641
00:28:54,980 --> 00:28:56,900
peaceful days are hard to come by.

642
00:28:58,539 --> 00:29:02,180
It relies on everyone's joint efforts.

643
00:29:02,739 --> 00:29:05,739
But a single rat dropping ruins the soup.

644
00:29:06,739 --> 00:29:09,980
First, bandits raided my humble home at night.

645
00:29:10,460 --> 00:29:12,180
Then, at the Fan family's,

646
00:29:12,499 --> 00:29:14,180
so much grain

647
00:29:14,339 --> 00:29:16,539
vanished overnight.

648
00:29:16,900 --> 00:29:18,019
Guard by day, guard by night,

649
00:29:18,180 --> 00:29:20,299
but a thief within is hard to guard against.

650
00:29:20,579 --> 00:29:22,059
I shouldn't have to say who.

651
00:29:25,380 --> 00:29:26,700
Fan Pengju!

652
00:29:27,579 --> 00:29:28,739
Turn around and face me.

653
00:29:30,900 --> 00:29:31,779
You!

654
00:29:32,339 --> 00:29:34,180
You are that rat dropping!

655
00:29:34,579 --> 00:29:35,180
You!

656
00:29:35,460 --> 00:29:36,779
You are that thief within!

657
00:29:38,380 --> 00:29:39,660
Fan Pengju.

658
00:29:40,499 --> 00:29:42,739
One look at the handwriting proves it wasn't you.

659
00:29:43,900 --> 00:29:45,579
Was it someone else?

660
00:29:45,860 --> 00:29:47,299
You need to understand,

661
00:29:48,099 --> 00:29:50,620
is it thievery or banditry?

662
00:29:52,380 --> 00:29:53,259
Patriarch Fan,

663
00:29:53,579 --> 00:29:55,140
don't be anxious.

664
00:29:55,460 --> 00:29:58,220
If he names his accomplices and isn't a bandit,

665
00:29:58,860 --> 00:30:00,140
he can avoid the death penalty.

666
00:30:00,460 --> 00:30:01,539
If he doesn't confess,

667
00:30:01,660 --> 00:30:03,660
then he'll be treated as a bandit collaborator.

668
00:30:04,980 --> 00:30:08,700
This is the rule you set yourself, sir.

669
00:30:09,860 --> 00:30:11,140
Those who collaborate with bandits,

670
00:30:14,140 --> 00:30:14,940
are buried alive.

671
00:30:18,380 --> 00:30:19,700
I wrote the words.

672
00:30:20,779 --> 00:30:22,579
I sent the signal too.

673
00:30:22,980 --> 00:30:24,860
Good people can do bad things,

674
00:30:25,339 --> 00:30:28,099
so why can't bad people do good things?

675
00:30:28,380 --> 00:30:29,660
Fan Pengju!

676
00:30:30,339 --> 00:30:31,380
You're talking nonsense!

677
00:30:31,380 --> 00:30:33,059
Do you know the consequences?

678
00:30:33,660 --> 00:30:34,940
A life is at stake!

679
00:30:35,180 --> 00:30:36,779
Under these circumstances,

680
00:30:36,779 --> 00:30:38,499
you're still spouting rubbish!

681
00:30:38,779 --> 00:30:40,339
You need to be clear,

682
00:30:40,739 --> 00:30:42,900
thief or bandit?

683
00:30:43,259 --> 00:30:44,819
Make it clear!

684
00:30:45,700 --> 00:30:47,059
Me and my brothers,

685
00:30:47,700 --> 00:30:49,940
we bow to Heaven, Earth, and Guan Gong.

686
00:30:50,779 --> 00:30:52,980
Enforcing justice for Heaven, supported by all.

687
00:30:53,099 --> 00:30:55,620
Killing the rich to aid the poor, the Brotherhood.

688
00:30:56,180 --> 00:30:58,380
The poor folks all say we're right.

689
00:30:58,499 --> 00:31:01,380
We are an army of chivalry.

690
00:31:04,700 --> 00:31:06,819
So you admit to collaborating with bandits.

691
00:31:08,220 --> 00:31:08,900
Patriarch.

692
00:31:09,299 --> 00:31:10,099
Patriarch.

693
00:31:10,620 --> 00:31:11,739
Sha'er didn't mean that.

694
00:31:11,980 --> 00:31:12,779
He didn't collaborate with bandits.

695
00:31:12,900 --> 00:31:14,180
He really didn't collaborate.

696
00:31:15,099 --> 00:31:15,940
Granduncle!

697
00:31:17,819 --> 00:31:18,860
He brought this sin on himself,

698
00:31:19,860 --> 00:31:20,700
he cannot live.

699
00:31:21,700 --> 00:31:22,499
Let him go.

700
00:31:24,420 --> 00:31:25,339
Silly child.

701
00:31:25,779 --> 00:31:26,900
He already admitted his guilt.

702
00:31:33,339 --> 00:31:34,739
All rise!

703
00:31:37,739 --> 00:31:38,940
Take him to the execution ground!

704
00:31:40,660 --> 00:31:41,339
Sha'er!

705
00:31:42,019 --> 00:31:42,700
Sha'er!

706
00:31:43,019 --> 00:31:43,620
Sha'er!

707
00:31:44,299 --> 00:31:45,819
Sha'er, you can't go!

708
00:31:45,940 --> 00:31:47,860
What will I do if you leave?

709
00:31:47,940 --> 00:31:48,819
Yuzhen.

710
00:31:48,980 --> 00:31:51,059
Stop crying and wiping your tears.

711
00:31:51,259 --> 00:31:52,259
Like this,

712
00:31:52,259 --> 00:31:54,900
how can I be a hero?

713
00:31:54,900 --> 00:31:55,499
Move!

714
00:31:55,940 --> 00:31:57,339
Then I won't live either!

715
00:31:57,539 --> 00:31:59,140
I'll go with you!

716
00:31:59,460 --> 00:32:01,099
Let go!

717
00:32:01,180 --> 00:32:01,819
Move!

718
00:32:01,900 --> 00:32:02,380
Sha'er!

719
00:32:02,380 --> 00:32:03,700
Stay strong!

720
00:32:04,140 --> 00:32:04,819
Move!

721
00:32:04,940 --> 00:32:07,460
Sha'er! Sha'er! Sha'er!

722
00:32:09,019 --> 00:32:09,739
Young Mistress!

723
00:32:09,819 --> 00:32:10,460
Young Mistress!

724
00:32:11,059 --> 00:32:11,779
Young Mistress!

725
00:32:13,579 --> 00:32:18,900
I hate Yang Guang for slaying the loyal,

726
00:32:25,620 --> 00:32:32,940
slanderous ministers are in power.

727
00:32:34,460 --> 00:32:41,860
Thinking of my parents, I cannot help it,

728
00:32:44,180 --> 00:32:52,579
tears soak my battle robe.

729
00:33:02,420 --> 00:33:04,259
A misfortune for the family

730
00:33:05,539 --> 00:33:07,259
To have birthed this vile spawn

731
00:33:08,660 --> 00:33:10,460
Of improper conduct

732
00:33:11,140 --> 00:33:13,140
Betraying his own kin

733
00:33:13,660 --> 00:33:15,739
Unrepentant despite discipline

734
00:33:16,259 --> 00:33:18,739
Self-exiled from the Fan clan

735
00:33:19,140 --> 00:33:21,259
To pacify the region

736
00:33:21,739 --> 00:33:24,339
Capital punishment: live burial

737
00:33:24,620 --> 00:33:27,980
Capital punishment: live burial

738
00:33:28,259 --> 00:33:30,940
Patriarch, you must think this through

739
00:33:31,259 --> 00:33:32,460
Let's not talk about that

740
00:33:33,700 --> 00:33:34,940
I blame neither heaven nor earth

741
00:33:34,940 --> 00:33:36,339
Nor do I blame myself

742
00:33:36,819 --> 00:33:38,140
I've lived this long

743
00:33:39,539 --> 00:33:40,339
Today

744
00:33:40,980 --> 00:33:42,819
I'll go out in style for once

745
00:33:44,539 --> 00:33:47,499
Everyone has to die sooner or later

746
00:33:48,420 --> 00:33:51,299
Rather than leave weeping and wailing

747
00:33:51,620 --> 00:33:53,660
I'd prefer to die happily

748
00:33:53,940 --> 00:33:55,499
In eighteen years

749
00:33:55,819 --> 00:33:57,539
I'll be a hero again

750
00:34:03,019 --> 00:34:04,779
Which blind fool dug this?

751
00:34:05,499 --> 00:34:06,499
It's so shallow

752
00:34:06,700 --> 00:34:09,299
It won't be worth it if dogs dig me up later

753
00:34:09,539 --> 00:34:10,099
Brother

754
00:34:11,259 --> 00:34:13,019
Dig deeper. Do me a favor, dig deeper

755
00:34:13,019 --> 00:34:13,940
Young Master

756
00:34:14,219 --> 00:34:15,860
Young Master

757
00:34:15,940 --> 00:34:16,940
Young Master!

758
00:34:16,940 --> 00:34:18,460
I've failed you!

759
00:34:18,460 --> 00:34:19,980
What are you crying for?

760
00:34:23,940 --> 00:34:24,900
Let me tell you

761
00:34:25,139 --> 00:34:26,740
When I jump down in a moment

762
00:34:27,019 --> 00:34:28,219
And lie flat

763
00:34:28,260 --> 00:34:30,099
Only then can you cover me with dirt

764
00:34:30,499 --> 00:34:31,300
Do you hear me?

765
00:34:31,900 --> 00:34:33,659
Fan Pengju

766
00:34:34,340 --> 00:34:37,300
You really are a fool

767
00:34:41,300 --> 00:34:42,499
You're the fool

768
00:34:44,019 --> 00:34:46,099
You smashed the incense burner

769
00:34:46,539 --> 00:34:47,820
When you die later

770
00:34:48,740 --> 00:34:50,900
No one will carry your spirit tablet

771
00:35:06,420 --> 00:35:07,699
Darn it

772
00:35:08,579 --> 00:35:11,940
Lost my life over a finger-guessing game

773
00:35:13,300 --> 00:35:14,099
Not worth it

774
00:35:17,420 --> 00:35:19,139
Young Master
